author: Russ Held, Special to The Republican
title: Manchester CC's Jordan Gosler wins 25th Connecticut Section PGA Match Play Championship
text: Manchester CC's Jordan Gosler wins 25th Connecticut Section PGA Match Play Championship IMG_20151015_113548_418.jpg Connecticut Section PGA Match Play Championship winner Jordan Gosler, third from left, poses with the Bob Kay Trophy Thursday at Goodwin Park Golf Course in Hartford. Pictured (left to right) are Patrick Aldrich, the Section's Golf Properties Consultant, Section Executive Director Tom Hantke, Section Operations and Player Development Manager Joe Mentz, PGA Life Member John Korolyshun and Goodwin Park golf professional Kevin Cloud. (Russ Held photo)
